org.linqs.psl.util

Class Parallel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.linqs.psl.util.Parallel

  • public final class Parallel
extends Object
    Utilities to run operations in parallel. The threads will be started up on the first call, and not shut down until the JVM shuts down. Since the thread pool (and CPU) is shared, only one task may be run in parallel at a time.
